### Alerts API Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Analyze a flow — DDoS profile
# This is the main endpoint: ML + LLM + MITRE in one call
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Analyze DDoS-like flow with source IP
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "features": {
    "flow_duration": 1000,
    "total_fwd_packets": 50000,
    "total_backward_packets": 0,
    "total_length_of_fwd_packets": 3000000,
    "flow_bytes_per_s": 3000000000,
    "flow_packets_per_s": 50000000,
    "flow_iat_mean": 20,
    "flow_iat_std": 5,
    "syn_flag_count": 50000,
    "ack_flag_count": 0,
    "fwd_packet_length_mean": 60,
    "init_win_bytes_forward": 1024,
    "init_win_bytes_backward": 0
  },
  "source_ip": "185.220.101.1",
  "destination_ip": "10.0.0.1",
  "destination_port": 80
}

###

### Analyze port scan profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "features": {
    "flow_duration": 500,
    "total_fwd_packets": 1,
    "total_backward_packets": 0,
    "flow_bytes_per_s": 100,
    "flow_packets_per_s": 2000,
    "syn_flag_count": 1,
    "ack_flag_count": 0,
    "fin_flag_count": 0,
    "rst_flag_count": 1,
    "destination_port": 22
  },
  "source_ip": "45.33.32.156",
  "destination_ip": "10.0.0.5",
  "destination_port": 22
}

###

### Analyze clean traffic — should not generate LLM call
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "features": {
    "flow_duration": 1000000,
    "total_fwd_packets": 10,
    "total_backward_packets": 8,
    "flow_bytes_per_s": 9000,
    "flow_packets_per_s": 18,
    "syn_flag_count": 1,
    "ack_flag_count": 17,
    "fin_flag_count": 1,
    "init_win_bytes_forward": 65535,
    "init_win_bytes_backward": 65535
  },
  "source_ip": "8.8.8.8",
  "destination_port": 443
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# List and manage alerts
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all recent alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts

###

### List only malicious alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts?verdict=malicious

###

### List critical severity, open status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts?severity=critical&status=open

###

### Get single alert (replace 1 with an actual ID from list)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/1

###

### Acknowledge an alert
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "acknowledged"
}

###

### Escalate an alert
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "escalated"
}

###

### Dismiss an alert
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "dismissed"
}
